Summary: I witnessed a green glowing u shaped object flying south.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing outside and i saw a light and looked up and saw a green u shaped object flying not to high over head. i yelled for my friends and and three seconds later a half mile away it dissapeared. it didnt fly off it just went away. it made no noise and had no flying pattern just straight. as soon as i saw it i yelled and it seemed to react to the yell and immediatly dissapeared. i was frightened and couldnt move from fear.
